40,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T23:52:42.000Z","msg":"又係中醫撚喺度呃神騙鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c7a1859f4c95bfdeef46250721e177ed17ada5","tid":1134940,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c4de5bbd4a4810219386944d166c683501e514","tid":1134940,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f2695aa2ac77fc954ad7f98d3475a865e99219d","tid":1134940,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:17:38.000Z","msg":"舒筋活絡嘅武術？<br />\n練蔡李佛啦<br />\n啲招根本就係拉筋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T23:35:45.000Z","msg":"八段錦<br />\n出名d啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"八段錦唔係武術"},{"pid":"5fefc08fda950ced08cdb030280524ca9c112214","tid":1134940,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e86932027807d15784b1bbc5d4566afc81ba36a","tid":1134940,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T23:52:42.000Z","msg":"又係中醫撚喺度呃神騙鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"你唔好理<br />\n總之中醫就係要好撚隱世好撚神秘先至有料到<br />\n咁勁既高手<br />\n都要淨係屈係邪骨場度幫啲有緣既虧佬玉莖重生<br />\n證明真係觀世音再世慾海慈航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764752a22c8197d0b36ef3172188823e705ade94","tid":1134940,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fefc08fda950ced08cdb030280524ca9c112214","tid":1134940,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e86932027807d15784b1bbc5d4566afc81ba36a","tid":1134940,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T23:52:42.000Z","msg":"又係中醫撚喺度呃神騙鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"你唔好理<br />\n總之中醫就係要好撚隱世好撚神秘先至有料到<br />\n咁勁既高手<br />\n都要淨係屈係邪骨場度幫啲有緣既虧佬玉莖重生<br />\n證明真係觀世音再世慾海慈航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"咪同煮野食一樣囉<br />\n點解好食既小炒，依家唔容易食得返<br />\n中醫係好多神棍出黎做壞巿<br />\n而且中醫又唔係萬能，只係勁在調養身體<br />\n<br />\n中醫有傳過去歐洲，現代醫學亦有參照過<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/rex28jr.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Frex28jr.html&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=cdd89c6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/rex28jr.html</a><br />\n<br />\n如果無其他國家保留住中國以前既文化、歴史、同傳統技藝，依家會以為所有源自中國野都係騙人<br />\n共最絕既係死不認錯，再用假貨充真貨去淡化佢既罪行<br />\n試下篇尋世界，搵下被文革消除而又在中國復興既技藝<br />\n會發現中國有既根本唔係同一版本<br />\n而且中國依家既西醫仲恐佈（咁唔通西醫又係騙局）"}]}